00:17:08,010 --> 00:17:13,210
So I'm very happy to introduce a new product we built called Brevis Vera.

208
00:17:13,210 --> 00:17:20,010
We're trying to solve a very critical problem in Brevis Vera today, that is if you see a

209
00:17:20,010 --> 00:17:29,290
viral media, like a viral photo or viral movie or video online, the first question now you

