00:17:49,290 --> 00:17:55,450
arms race because you never can beat an AI with another AI.

214
00:17:55,450 --> 00:18:02,170
So what we're here trying to do is to provide a different solution that enables you to generate

215
00:18:02,170 --> 00:18:04,410
a test station of what is real.

216
00:18:04,410 --> 00:18:10,290
So we're not detecting what is fake, we're actually testing what is real.

